- **Conservative**: 14-20% (4-6 ms reduction) → target ~24 ms
- **Optimistic**: 20-27% (6-8 ms reduction) → target ~21-23 ms
- **Target**: Close 60% of the 10 ms gap vs DuckDB (29.3 → 21-23 ms)

